---
import Container from "../components/Container.astro";
import { BookOpen } from "@lucide/astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<section>
  <Container>
    <div
      class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-800 rounded-2xl flex-1 flex flex-col space-y-6 px-16 py-16 text-center justify-center"
    >
      <div class="flex text-center justify-center">
        <div class="text-gray-200">
          <BookOpen size="60" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <span class="text-white text-3xl font-bold"
        >Juntos podemos llevar la Palabra a cada pueblo</span
      >
      <span class="text-gray-200 text-xl max-w-6xl"
        >Tu participación, ya sea a través de la oración, donación o servicio,
        es fundamental para cumplir la Gran Comisión en los pueblos de
        Latinoamérica.</span
      >
      <div class="pt-6">
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 py-3">
          <div class="text-center">
            <a
              href="/impacto"
              class="inline-flex bg-white hover:bg-gray-200 items-center justify-center text-blue-600 font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg"
            >
              Contactanos
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <a
              href="/impacto"
              class="inline-flex bg-blue-600 hover:bg-white hover:text-blue-600 text-white border-2 border-white items-center justify-center font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg"
            >
              Más Información
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
